solution: ```class Solution {
    public int binaryGap(int n) {
        int max = 0;
        int last = -1;
        int pos = 0;
        while (n != 0) {
            if ((n & 1) == 1) {
                if (last != -1) {
                    max = Math.max(max, pos - last);
                }
                last = pos;
            }
            pos++;
            n >>>= 1;
        }
        return max;
    }
}
```
